T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on potential-difference reasoning.) Tj
T*
(2. Break the task into smaller parts and link each part to the rule being used.) Tj
T*
(3. Point out how to avoid confusing voltage with current while solving it.) Tj
T*
(4. Review the result and connect it back to the topic overview.) Tj
